          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Men have gaped at me with their mouth; they have struck me insolently on the cheek; they mass themselves together against me. "
