          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I was at ease, and he broke me apart; he seized me by the neck and dashed me to pieces; he set me up as his target; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I was at ease, and he broke me apart; he seized me by the neck and dashed me to pieces; he set me up as his target;"
