          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "his archers surround me. He slashes open my kidneys and does not spare; he pours out my gall on the ground. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
